dct_title_s: San Diego natural color ortho mosaic image
dct_alternative_sm: San Diego Co. 2-ft ortho mosaic CIR converted to "natural color"
San Diego County 2-foot ortho mosaic color infrared converted to "natural color"
dct_description_sm: "Contains a mosaic image of San Diego County, Calif. color orthoimages in ECW compressed image format. The original color infrared (CIR) imagery was processed to create a synthetic "natural color" version of the imagery ... The ECW image can be viewed in any application that supports the ECW format. This DVD contains plug-ins for several common applications that do not provide native ECW support ... The ER Viewer software application is also provided"--Readme file.
Uncompressed file size: 116.37 GB (ECW compressed file size: 3.87 GB).
"Date created: October, 2002"--Readme file (source data is from 2001).
System requirements: PC; software that supports the ECW compressed image format (plugins and standalone software included).
